re it is needed most. The trapping\nof energy by the cold gas may provide an additional feedback mechanism that\nhelps to regulate the heating of the central regions of galaxy clusters and\ncouple the AGN to the ICM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Jan 2008 21:36:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Feb 2008 10:45:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
