i = 6.4 \\pm 1.9 mas (i.e. 156 \\pm 50 pc) and for the GQ Lup companion\nto be 7.2 \\pm 2.1 mas (i.e. 139 \\pm 45 pc), both consistent with being in the\nLupus I cloud and bound to each other.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2008 13:11:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
