the case of periodic domains under\neither Dirichlet or Robin boundary conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Jan 2008 13:27:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 6 Jun 2009 08:44:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
